# Overview

## Default Model

- qwen2.5:7b

## Runtime Settings

- temperature: 0.2
- top_p: 0.9
- num_ctx: 4096

## Mandatory Prompt Header

Return only valid JSON.
No text.
No markdown.
No explanations.

## Enforcement Rules

- Always pass a schema.
- Always set max tokens.
- Reject responses with:
  - Leading text
  - Trailing text
  - Invalid JSON

## n8n Integration Rules

- One request per task.
- No multi-turn state.
- Validate output before use.

## Fallback Strategy

- Retry once with stricter wording.
- If still invalid, return structured error.

## Forbidden

- Free-form prose.
- Mixed output types.
- Implicit formatting.

